{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools to make pupils wear PE kit in place of traditional uniform",
        "additional_details": "We believe that wearing PE kits to school will allow students to be more comfortable in lessons, which will help with their learning and behaviour in school and help families with the cost of living crisis.",
        "background": "We want the government to mandate that all schools must make pupils wear PE kit (polo shirts and tracksuit bottoms) rather than shirts and ties.",
